Count.ly
How will we use your data?
Our company collects your data so that we can:
Manage your account
Send you notifications about special events and notices
How is the data stored?
Our company securely stores your data in France (Europe).
Our company will keep your personal information for 12 months. On this time period has expired, we will delete your data by deleting your user account.
Device model (anonymous)
